  "text": "We train Resnet-18 [CITATION_1] on CIFAR-10 (50000 training samples with labels) for over 200 epochs using an initial learning rate of 0.05 with the decaying schedule of factor 5 after every 90 epochs. The reported accuracy is based on the true validation set. The results of the CIFAR-10 dataset are averaged over 3 runs. Lastly, in Fig. 4 , we show that for a neural network MKL-SGD typically has a higher training loss but smaller test loss which partially explains its superior generalization performance. ",
